Make R objects pasteable

Source: R/pasteable.R
pasteable.Rd

Make R objects pasteable

Usage

pasteable(x, target = c("sheet", "chat"))

Arguments

x

A data.frame or list.

target

Where you will paste the content.

Value

A length 1 character vector.

Examples

# Meaningful row names are kept
pasteable(mtcars)
